si.title: கர்ப்பத்துக்கு யார் அப்பா? படத்துடன் கருவி
body_lines: Who is a baby that grows in the stomach of the woman if a woman is pregnant? මෙම පුවත සමාජ මාධ්යවල වෛරස් වන අතර, ගර්භනී මෙවලමෙහි ඡායාරූපයක් සහිතව, පියාට පෙන්වීමට මෙවලමක් පළ කරමින්.

en.title: Who is the father of pregnancy? Tool with the picture
body_lines: Who is a baby that grows in the stomach of the woman if a woman is pregnant? This news is going viral on social media, with a photo of the pregnant tool, posting a tool to show the father.
